snippet.title: How to Pronounce Amber Heard? (CORRECTLY)
snippet.description:
Learn more celebrity name pronunciations: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nlzHzGRJoYc&list=PLd_ydU7Boqa1fQGqaJNavBgb92MKqDsdq
Listen how to say Amber Heard correctly (celebrity name, Johnny Depp) with Julien, "how do you pronounce" free pronunciation audio/video tutorials.

Who is Amber Heard? Amber Heard American actress Description
Amber Laura Heard is an American actress and model. Born and raised in Texas, she made her film debut in a minor supporting role in the sports drama Friday Night Lights, followed by a series of other small roles in television and film. Wikipedia Source: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amber_Heard
Born: April 22, 1986 (age 34 years), Austin, Texas, United States
Height: 1.7 m
Partner: Tasya van Ree (2008–2012)
Spouse: Johnny Depp (m. 2015–2017)
Parents: Paige Parsons, David Heard
Movies and TV shows
Aquaman (2018)
The Playboy Club (2011)
Criminal Minds (2005 – 2020)
Hidden Palms (2007)
The Rum Diary (2011)
Profiles Instagram Twitter Facebook
People also search for
Amber Heard and Nicole Kidman appear in Aquaman.
Nicole Kidman
Trending
Amber Heard and Johnny Depp were married for one year (until 2017). Amber Heard appears in and Johnny Depp produced The Rum Diary.
Johnny Depp Former spouse
Amber Heard and Tasya van Ree were partners for 4 years (until 2012).
Tasya van Ree
Former partner
Lori Anne Allison
Lily‑Rose Depp

Learn how to say words in English, French, Spanish, German, Italian, and many other languages with Julien Miquel and his pronunciation tutorials! In the world of words and the diversity of accents and local dialects, some words can be extremely hard to pronounce.

Julien’s instructional and educational videos make pronunciation easier as I detail the correct pronunciation as native French speaker but also fluent speaker of French, English, Spanish and Italian.
-If you found this video helpful please like the video to support my work.
-If you would like help with any future pronunciations please be sure to subscribe!
-Thanks for Watching How To Pronounce with Julien and happy pronouncing.
